Package: BayesPortfolio
Type: Package
Title: Factor Investing: A Bayesian Hierarchical Approach
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-07-23
Author: Jingyu He, Gavin Guanhao Feng
Maintainer: Jingyu He <jingyuhe@cityu.edu.hk>
Description: This package implements the method from Factor Investing: A Bayesian Hierarchical Approach. It provide a seemingly regression model with hierarchical prior to model multiple assets, predict stock returns and estimate covariance matrix. Thus build mean-variance efficient portfolio.
License: Apache License (== 2.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
NeedsCompilation: yes